Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.20,0:00:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.50,0:00:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安佳美 這位是我的親戚溫子姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.71,0:00:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫做溫子 請多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.46,0:00:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就叫妳溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.43,0:00:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫荻原佳美 請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.93,0:00:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.05,0:00:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 還有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.72,0:00:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸工作很忙不能去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.39,0:00:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不能開車子去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.98,0:00:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.40,0:00:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就搭電車去嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.57,0:00:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就交給我來辦好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.73,0:00:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.24,0:00:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是這個是 腳踏車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.07,0:00:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.91,0:00:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是搭電車去的話 也需要三個鐘頭呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.04,0:00:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有問題的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.71,0:00:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能比電車還要快也說不定 對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.29,0:00:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.28,0:02:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.32,0:02:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.87,0:02:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,0K OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.74,0:02:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳美你OK了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.54,0:02:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啦 可是... 真的不要緊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.66,0:02:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊 不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.42,0:03:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子可以出發啦 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.54,0:03:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.71,0:03:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子要出發啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.68,0:03:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經聽說啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.72,0:03:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海水浴場道件事 我絕對反對到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.56,0:03:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有在聽我說呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.02,0:03:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對反對你呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.89,0:03:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有沒有聽我說話呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.69,0:03:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.48,0:03:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然讓龍之介去海邊 我絕對不允許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.07,0:03:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼會知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.24,0:03:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有關那孩子的事情 我什麽都很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.62,0:03:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了吧 你記著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.58,0:03:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像海邊這樣的地方呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.12,0:03:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼膀胱炎啦膽囊炎啦 還有腹膜炎啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.29,0:03:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,造成這些病因的大腸菌 很多很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.29,0:03:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,造成皮膚癌原因的紫外線 也大量的照射下來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.04,0:03:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有很多的空氣、髒空氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.26,0:03:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空罐瓶子啦玻璃瓶啦 對身體很不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.01,0:03:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼危險也讓孩子去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.64,0:03:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個老爸到底是怎麼當的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.60,0:03:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有資格做父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.27,0:04:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的愛比獸類還不如
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.35,0:04:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介這孩子根本就不能交給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.23,0:04:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣保護的話 才會損害小孩的健康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.07,0:04:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海水浴是很好的活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.45,0:04:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘量玩 一定要好好的玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.78,0:04:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是教育孩子的我一貫的作風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.20,0:04:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說的話 假如龍之介有了什麼意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.21,0:04:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你要怎麼負責？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.04,0:04:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會發生事情的 因為溫子也一起去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.22,0:04:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這種機器人 根本就不能讓人信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.47,0:04:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的設計是非常完善的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.10,0:04:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們絕對會受傷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.56,0:04:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.18,0:04:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果受傷就要你負責 聽到沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.81,0:04:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那有什麼問題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.39,0:04:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧！那我就答應你 讓他去海邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.61,0:04:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要是我們的寶貝兒子 有了什麼傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.28,0:04:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從此以後我就要領回龍之介 由我來養育
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.62,0:04:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到了沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.83,0:05:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶子 這是兩回事呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 沒想到妳真行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.17,0:05:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子的話 龍之介少爺就會回去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.67,0:05:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.55,0:05:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到海邊去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.18,0:05:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在游泳的時候 我們偷偷得靠過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.18,0:05:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用針或是什麽東西刺一下的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.85,0:05:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.85,0:05:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 用針刺他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.60,0:05:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳想讓我的兒子受傷是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.15,0:05:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.69,0:05:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他說好的不是這個意思嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.23,0:05:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能對孩子道麼做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我擔心起來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.95,0:05:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把車子準備好 快點！會影響年終獎金的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.66,0:05:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.42,0:05:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到啦！ 在這裡行吧 龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.80,0:05:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡可以嗎？佳美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.81,0:06:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 我們到得很早吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.39,0:06:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是好像在坐快速滑行車上面兩個小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.40,0:06:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.73,0:06:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸一叔叔 我是佳美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.78,0:06:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.70,0:06:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.62,0:06:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來打擾你啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.92,0:06:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸一叔叔 怎麼了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.97,0:06:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上來 馬上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.31,0:06:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓大家久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.69,0:06:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！現在陪大家到海邊玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.37,0:07:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是海啊 我是第一次看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.75,0:07:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那個地方可以抓到魚嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.37,0:07:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要抓好多好多的魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.04,0:07:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚？你們喜歡抓魚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.75,0:07:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀 可是這是我第一次抓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.21,0:07:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是蟲和老鼠的話 我常常都在抓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.52,0:07:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 你太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.52,0:07:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.32,0:07:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.82,0:07:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩子都很天真很可愛呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.66,0:07:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很快樂 真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.37,0:07:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.66,0:07:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人應該在海邊 優雅的曬太陽才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.62,0:07:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎？真沒意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.50,0:07:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有準備防曬油 我來替你服務一下好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.84,0:07:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,油？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊！讓我來好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.18,0:08:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要我幫你擦一擦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.39,0:08:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.06,0:08:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.32,0:08:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我還是去游泳好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.75,0:08:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.59,0:08:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好燙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.86,0:08:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.25,0:09:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦！現在我去游泳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.71,0:09:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.14,0:09:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子姐姐可能不會游泳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.89,0:09:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會啦！雖然是頭一次游泳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.69,0:09:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是她不可能是個秤錘啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.65,0:09:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了！那個傢伙的身體不會浮在水面上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.17,0:10:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇！震憾 震憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.30,0:10:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是機械身 沒有想到完全不會浮在水面上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.18,0:10:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不幸發現了機器人NK1124的弱點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.02,0:10:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我要把那隻貓小姐 弄得她吃不消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.07,0:10:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊！這就是久作的傻氣 所以我才不能放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.32,0:10:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 那個女孩可以利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.16,0:10:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳的意思是說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.08,0:10:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓那女孩子來打動龍之介的心房 妳們看怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.22,0:11:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮！如果可以搭這種船周遊世界不知道多好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.72,0:11:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 我有個禮物要送給佳美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.56,0:11:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好呀！你看不是很適合妳嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.82,0:11:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是妳是陌生人 我不能拿這麼高價的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.65,0:11:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是外人 龍之介他是我的孩子呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.33,0:11:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.74,0:12:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我因為有某種原因 跟我丈夫分開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.08,0:12:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果妳將來跟龍之介結婚的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.78,0:12:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不就成了婆媳了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.92,0:12:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以這件衣服妳應該可以很放心的收下了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.01,0:12:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 伯母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.93,0:12:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我伯母真是太見外了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.39,0:12:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我媽媽好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.56,0:12:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.53,0:12:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再吃魚啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.30,0:12:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介 龍之介你起來嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.34,0:12:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介我們去看看黎明的海邊嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.39,0:12:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想睡呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.97,0:13:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.20,0:13:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不見呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.79,0:13:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們到海邊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.09,0:13:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳美她究竟跑到什麽地方去了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.22,0:13:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在她一定正在吃香噴噴的早餐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.06,0:13:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.27,0:13:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許在什麼地方和她走散了也不一定呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.77,0:13:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.67,0:14:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.88,0:14:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到佳美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.21,0:14:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看那船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.42,0:14:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那艘船是散卡利花號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.05,0:14:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.22,0:14:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我媽的遊艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.14,0:14:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.07,0:14:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺請快點上船吧 你媽媽正等著你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.28,0:14:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太卑鄙了！ 妳把佳美抓走當人質好可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.08,0:14:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這樣呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.50,0:14:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她自己喜歡上來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.50,0:14:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.04,0:14:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你自己來問問她好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.05,0:14:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看一下好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.93,0:14:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.68,0:15:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡沒有妳的位子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.51,0:15:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果妳想來了 妳就自己游泳過來好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.23,0:15:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是秤錘 那就困難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.78,0:15:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子 溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.95,0:15:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介！ 龍之介！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.54,0:15:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.75,0:15:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.55,0:15:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三島重工業製造的裝甲章魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.43,0:15:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回報妳那一次的禮物 機械人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.37,0:16:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.50,0:16:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.17,0:16:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超級越野車 出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.44,0:16:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.77,0:16:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要緊？溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.78,0:16:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 龍之介 龍之介他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.08,0:16:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.37,0:16:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子不會游泳 不會浮起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.47,0:17:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸這是什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.22,0:17:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子的話 妳就海豚一樣的游泳直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.68,0:17:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是機械美人魚RX73
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.81,0:17:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.69,0:17:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.57,0:18:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.95,0:18:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有沒有受傷呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.66,0:18:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天有沒有按時吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.29,0:18:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有準時洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.62,0:18:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像被太陽曬黑了點兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.62,0:18:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該要擦點防曬油才對嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.88,0:18:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起來還是很健康的樣子 媽媽放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.92,0:18:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還給我 把佳美快點還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.64,0:18:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介 媽媽跟佳美說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.81,0:18:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們三個人生活在一起怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.65,0:18:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,商量的結果佳美她也很贊成媽媽的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.15,0:18:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.19,0:18:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳美她絕對不可能說這樣子的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.45,0:18:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是媽媽妳在說假話騙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.62,0:18:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的 龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.25,0:18:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳美！人家都在擔心妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.04,0:19:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.01,0:19:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 這件衣服很漂亮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.05,0:19:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳怎麼搞的呀 佳美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.10,0:19:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想跟媽媽還有龍之介三個人生活在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.81,0:19:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀 當然是這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.77,0:19:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.90,0:19:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.29,0:19:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 我們一塊來喝茶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.71,0:19:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.46,0:19:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.88,0:19:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來接你回去的！走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.76,0:19:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子 妳會游泳了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.76,0:19:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸來啦 他讓我會游泳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.47,0:19:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.94,0:20:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳老是糾纏不休
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.20,0:20:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機器人妳到底能夠耐多大的水壓呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.59,0:20:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壞掉好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.76,0:20:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭章魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.99,0:20:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.62,0:21:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解決了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.13,0:21:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.19,0:22:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扭斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.03,0:22:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.53,0:22:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.01,0:22:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.40,0:22:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太...太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.52,0:22:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.86,0:22:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.95,0:23:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.63,0:23:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油呀 龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.05,0:23:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.44,0:23:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.40,0:23:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎...怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.45,0:23:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會痛呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.79,0:23:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這只是一點小傷而已 不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.67,0:23:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想妳不會怎記吧 主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.13,0:23:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如龍之介少爺受傷的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.30,0:23:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們約好了要把龍之介少爺還給太太的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.97,0:24:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.56,0:24:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時講話的情勢使我 怎麼說呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.43,0:24:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.44,0:24:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼！妳放開我！放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.23,0:24:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.44,0:24:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.15,0:24:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.33,0:24:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是為了救我而受傷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.54,0:24:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子的話我怎麼能把他帶回去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.63,0:24:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.63,0:24:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這並不表示我已經放棄這孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.92,0:24:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如龍之介身上萬一有了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.47,0:24:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候我一定要把他帶回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.48,0:24:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該回去了 妳們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:54.65,0:24:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我們呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.96,0:25:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.13,0:25:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
